00:30:27,700 --> 00:30:30,967
I don't know. maybe he's lost his arm In
some kind of freak accident that Gretchen saw.

505
00:30:31,034 --> 00:30:34,000
- A double accident?
- yeah.

506
00:30:34,067 --> 00:30:37,334
That's him. that's the boy I saw.

507
00:30:37,401 --> 00:30:40,200
That's one-armed joe? That's
Clay Dennis, Gretchen's brother.

508
