511
00:30:45,833 --> 00:30:47,501
Well, if he wants to hang
onto the rest of his limbs,

512
00:30:47,566 --> 00:30:48,633
He'd better start talking.

513
00:30:52,666 --> 00:30:56,700
You know, the warning label on these
Says that you're not supposed to drive.

514
00:30:58,367 --> 00:30:59,733
I don't think that's a problem.

515
