I see spirits. I've seen your
sister. she's angry at you.

517
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:11,800
Ok. you saw my sister's ghost.

518
00:31:11,867 --> 00:31:14,633
Yes. And the fact that I talk to ghosts

519
00:31:14,700 --> 00:31:16,600
Is not something I like to admit

520
