And that same arm was
injured. missing, in fact.

526
00:31:34,134 --> 00:31:38,334
Ok, please stop. I know exactly
what you're talking about,

527
00:31:38,401 --> 00:31:40,467
But how...

528
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:47,566
Oh, my god.

529
