625
00:38:09,901 --> 00:38:11,933
But you can grant one more wish.

626
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:15,134
You can help your
brother forgive himself.

627
00:38:17,467 --> 00:38:22,467
All I ever wanted to do was be
with him. No matter what he did.

628
00:38:22,534 --> 00:38:26,667
She always looked up to you.
She wanted to be with you.

629
00:38:26,734 --> 00:38:28,800
But I was so mean to you.

630
00:38:29,966 --> 00:38:32,867
And you were just a kid.

631
00:38:32,933 --> 00:38:38,067
You were a kid, too. Will you tell
him I love him and forgive him?

632
00:38:38,334 --> 00:38:41,467
I will. She understands now.

633
00:38:41,534 --> 00:38:43,534
That it was a horrible accident.

634
00:38:47,634 --> 00:38:50,233
Same goes for you.

635
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:53,500
