641
00:39:10,267 --> 00:39:12,400
Still, I can't help but wishing...

642
00:39:12,467 --> 00:39:16,000
Wishing you did something
different. So does she.

643
00:39:16,066 --> 00:39:18,066
Who?

644
00:39:18,133 --> 00:39:20,667
The woman who left the note.

645
00:39:20,734 --> 00:39:24,467
The one who came here
With your daughter.

646
00:39:24,534 --> 00:39:28,634
Of course. The other note.

647
00:39:28,700 --> 00:39:30,434
"i wish that he could
know she was here. "

648
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:33,534
Wha... what other note?
what is she saying?

649
00:39:33,600 --> 00:39:36,933
I think she's talking
about your girlfriend,

650
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,000
Allison.

651
00:40:15,434 --> 00:40:18,834
12 years. and she'd been
living here the whole time.

652
00:40:18,901 --> 00:40:23,500
