It got harder to tell him.

658
00:40:34,667 --> 00:40:38,933
So, the visits to the well. I guess so.

659
00:40:40,933 --> 00:40:43,233
So far, so good. right.

660
00:40:47,567 --> 00:40:49,834
What? is she here?

661
00:40:49,901 --> 00:40:53,167
Figured while I'm here, I
might as well help people.

662
00:40:53,233 --> 00:40:56,966
Like your friend Sam. Sam?

663
00:40:57,033 --> 00:41:01,100
It was dark for so long.

664
00:41:01,167 --> 00:41:03,801
Now it's so warm and bright.

665
00:41:03,867 --> 00:41:06,400
