667
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:14,367
Something he really wanted.

668
00:41:14,434 --> 00:41:16,700
Turns out it was
something he already had.

669
00:41:16,767 --> 00:41:18,300
What?

670
00:41:18,367 --> 00:41:20,767
