671
00:41:36,534 --> 00:41:39,033
Which life?

672
00:41:47,567 --> 00:41:49,033
Thank you.

673
00:42:18,801 --> 00:42:22,100
It's been kind of a weird day, And I didn't
know who else I could talk to about it.

674
00:42:23,467 --> 00:42:24,966
Ok.

675
00:42:25,033 --> 00:42:29,333
I was going through all my
stuff, And I found a key.

676
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:33,434
I know it's strange, I've been
hoping... Wishing for a clue.

677
00:42:33,500 --> 00:42:37,233
Something to tell me who I was. Right?

678
00:42:43,167 --> 00:42:45,200
Guess I got more than I bargained for.

679
00:42:55,233 --> 00:42:57,367
Are you sure this belongs to you?

680
00:42:57,434 --> 00:43:01,100
Yeah. My name was right
